 <p>En partenariat avec le Conservatoire Henri Duparc de l''agglomération Tarbes-Lourdes-Pyrénées</p>  <p></p> ","type":"text","version":1}],"direction":"ltr","format":"","indent":0,"type":"paragraph","version":1}],"direction":"ltr","format":"","indent":0,"type":"root","version":1}}', NULL, 'en', '25e8db78-6d4f-4955-b0a0-63027506f493');
