abelle Avid de la compagnie Le Corps Sage.&nbsp;</p>  <p></p>  <p>Spectacle programmé dans le cadre des mercredis artistiques.</p> ","type":"text","version":1}],"direction":"ltr","format":"","indent":0,"type":"paragraph","version":1}],"direction":"ltr","format":"","indent":0,"type":"root","version":1}}', NULL, 'en', '47919f97-f021-42a4-9b10-311d917479a4');
