xt=\"true\">Jauge limitée à 49 places sans Pass sanitaire.</span></span></p> ","type":"text","version":1}],"direction":"ltr","format":"","indent":0,"type":"paragraph","version":1}],"direction":"ltr","format":"","indent":0,"type":"root","version":1}}', NULL, 'en', '16033f7f-4423-46bf-a4d7-3307f3928e9f');
