a Compagnie de la TONG, à qui on a donné \"Carte Blanche\" pour inventer trois créations vivantes et originales de restitution de ces paroles, regards croisés pour la perception locale d''un changement global !</p> ","type":"text","version":1}],"direction":"ltr","format":"","indent":0,"type":"paragraph","version":1}],"direction":"ltr","format":"","indent":0,"type":"root","version":1}}', NULL, 'en', '01a5ac27-ee26-471b-a5ca-3f6fbd1ff060');
