ormations :&nbsp;<br>  https://www.maisondelavallee.org/atelier-origami-sauvage-jonathan-rebouillat<br>  18h - Conférence, offerte, pour plus d''informations :&nbsp;<br>  https://www.maisondelavallee.org/conference-origami-sauvage-jonathan-rebouillat</p>  <p></p> ","type":"text","version":1}],"direction":"ltr","format":"","indent":0,"type":"paragraph","version":1}],"direction":"ltr","format":"","indent":0,"type":"root","version":1}}', NULL, 'en', 'e65a6895-ab1e-4aa1-b028-c7a219feda39');
