ustify;\">Salle de spectacle</p>  <p></p> ","type":"text","version":1}],"direction":"ltr","format":"","indent":0,"type":"paragraph","version":1}],"direction":"ltr","format":"","indent":0,"type":"root","version":1}}', NULL, 'en', 'b16b54d3-9771-4d0b-b53f-d9d706b4d9ea');
