</strong><br>  Dès 6 ans, 45min<br>  Cette séance est réservée aux écoles de la vallée</p>  <p style=\"text-align: justify;\"></p> ","type":"text","version":1}],"direction":"ltr","format":"","indent":0,"type":"paragraph","version":1}],"direction":"ltr","format":"","indent":0,"type":"root","version":1}}', NULL, 'en', '1f54bfea-33e4-4323-96d4-eff2756370ff');
